com.tangosol.coherence.dsltools.termtrees

Interface TermWalker

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractCoherenceQueryWalker, ConstructorQueryWalker, FilterBuilder, SelectListMaker, UpdateSetListMaker

    public interface TermWalker
    TermWalker is a visitor class that provides a framework for walking Term Trees
